styleCard.description: A soulful and rhythmic Ethio-jazz piece, combining traditional Ethiopian melodies with a driving funk rhythm, evoking the spirit of a road trip through the diverse landscapes and bustling streets from Addis Ababa to Oromia, with a hint of urban melancholy and discovery.

directions: Start at Addis Abeba, Addis Ababa
Turn right on Tesema Aba Kemaw Street
At the roundabout, take the second exit onto A5 (Gobena Aba Tigu Street)
At the roundabout, take the second exit to stay on A5
Turn left at Arbegnoch Street to stay on A4 (Arbegnoch Street)
At the roundabout, take the second exit to stay on A4 (Arbegnoch Street)
Turn left on A3 (Dejazmach Belay Zeleke Street)
At the roundabout, take the fourth exit to stay on A3 (Tunisia Street)
Finish at Degem, Selale, Oromia, on the right
